<br>
“You don’t get it do you?” she smiled at his back. “You assume too much. I will have you know that I never took any vow under Hera. I took a blood binding. As to the issue of my body, it is my heart and soul that belong to my lover. As for my loyalty, I never made a pass at you. Believe me, you would know if I did.”<br>
<br>
She was starting to get annoyed now. This man was judging her before he knew a thing about her. If he knew Hiroshi, he would understand everything, he was just proving himself ignorant to the ways of the world, and it saddened her.<br>
<br>
“Think about what I am. I am an amazon warrior with a husband and three children. I fight and kill for a living, and am an assassin by training. I am the head ambassador of Themisycra, the village you were born in. I was born a Roman noblewoman, and was a priestess for a time. You cannot define me, and please, do not try to judge me before you even know me.”<br>
<br>
Done, she sighed, knowing that in the end, she could not win. She would lose someone that would have been a friend to her just because she mentioned that she had a husband.<br>
<br>
&quot;I hope the army accepts you. But I will mourn the loss of a friend, someone that decided what they would think of me based purely on my status and my body. It is a shame.&quot;<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=theseusofthemiscrya>Theseus of Themiscrya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 97<br> <font color=#993300>(6/3/03 6:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm65.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/ixltheseuslxl/myhomepage/theseus1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just who is this girl?</span><hr size=1> Theseus looked at her utterly confused.  He had not judged her for it was not his place to judge but only the gods place to judge.  &quot;I have not judged you, forgive me if that is what you thought I had done.  However, regardless, I am in a very unbearable position.  By staying here in this place with you, the appearance of wrong doing is still present.&quot;  He moved to the door, &quot;I will not put Troy or Themiscrya in harms way by pretending that there is not something wrong here.  I am certainly happy for you that you have a husband and children.  I am happy for you that you are an ambassador and an assassin, but that makes my time with you further express the greatest need for caution.&quot;  He frowned at her, &quot;I never said you made a pass at me.  I am not that vain to believe that a woman such as yourself would have need for a boy like me.  And before you jump to any more conclusions and I waste anymore of your time, I believe I will take care of my business.  You may stay here as long as you like.  I will not deny an amazon shelter.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=battlingangel>Battling Angel</A></span><br>