<br>
&quot;You know something? Your mother must be incredibly proud to have a son like you.&quot; she smiled, though somewhat sadly. &quot;You certainly have a lot more wisdom than most people that I have met. And even though I have stayed with men before, and never had a trouble, if you truly do think that you will damage a reputation, you can do as you wish.&quot;<br>
<br>
Kalasin was glad that she had met this man. He was a wonderful person, and it restored her faith somewhat in human nature.<br>
<br>
&quot;I still expect you to show me around the city at some stage though&quot; she grinned widely. &quot;Now go, join the Trojan Army, they'll be glad to have someone like you in their ranks.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=theseusofthemiscrya>Theseus of Themiscrya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 98<br> <font color=#993300>(6/3/03 6:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm65.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/ixltheseuslxl/myhomepage/theseus1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just who is this girl?</span><hr size=1> Theseus shrugged lightly, &quot;I do not know how my mother feels about having a son like me; however, I believe like every good amazon, she would have preferred a daughter, one to follow in her footsteps and learn the amazon way.  But for some reason, Hera chose for her to have a son.&quot;  He opened the door to his room, thinking for a moment before he spoke again.  <br>
<br>
He cleared his throat and nodded towards the pack hanging on the wall.  &quot;There is some food in that pack.  Some cured meats and cheese.  A loaf of bread and even a loaf of nutbread.&quot;  He smiled slightly.  &quot;Please help yourself to the food.  I can get more, it's not a problem.&quot;  With that he pulled the door shut behind him giving her some privacy and time alone. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=battlingangel>Battling Angel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#993300>(6/3/03 9:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm65.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.speedis.org/images/214.png WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just who is this girl?</span><hr size=1> Kalasin frowned at the choice of foods that he had listed off. She was not hungry, then again, she rarely was. The amazon woman only ate when she had to.<br>
Right now, she felt like sleeping. According to her body, she had been travelling for nearly 4 days without a rest. It was high time that she actually got some. Without a sound, the amazon woman pulled the rought blanket off the bed and around her shoulder. She laid down on the floor at the foot of the bed, curled up, and dozed off for a while.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#993300>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#993300> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm65>Troy</a> <font color=#993300> - </font><a href="http://pub163.ezboard.com/bmythicalodysseyforum">Home</a><font color=#993300> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.3m<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

